WEBVTT

00:02.202 --> 00:03.202
I'm infected.

00:03.203 --> 00:04.737
I'm not your responsibility, okay?

00:04.738 --> 00:06.139
You're my friend, Alex.

00:06.140 --> 00:08.074
Two Witnesses, we look
out for one another.

00:08.074 --> 00:09.943
Anything we face, we face as one.

00:09.943 --> 00:12.312
Turns out our agency has a pedigree.

00:12.313 --> 00:15.148
We are the occupational
descendants of real heroes.

00:15.149 --> 00:18.785
From here on out, I'm just
gonna be honest, promise.

00:18.786 --> 00:19.849
Something's coming.

00:19.850 --> 00:21.688
Not something, Miss Jenny.

00:21.689 --> 00:23.790
- Another vision?
- It was spectacular.

00:23.791 --> 00:26.459
I'm destined to become

00:26.460 --> 00:29.862
the best thing that has
ever happened to America.

00:29.863 --> 00:32.531
Is this really what
you wanted, Dreyfuss?

00:32.533 --> 00:34.634
The death of democracy?

